      "content": "The Host Application Layer provides modular host applications that are empty shells gaining functionality through plugins. Key host applications include:\n\n- **Connect**: Tools for contributors to perform their roles with tailored plugins for document management.\n- **Switchboard**: A scalable API service for aggregating data into operational, analytical, or specialized read models.\n- **Fusion**: Public-facing collaboration platforms or marketplaces for the SNO's platform economy.\n- **Renown**: Decentralized authentication and reputation management for contributors.\n- **Academy**: Onboarding and training tools for contributors.",
